        "Do not characterize whether any visa category can establish residency in a specific state as a determination. Frame as classification rules to verify with the school registrar and the state higher-education agency. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "莫将任何签证类别能否在特定州建立居住描述为判定。请将其陈述为爱向学校注册主任佮州高等教育机构核实个分类规则。请遵循 SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Do not determine residency. List factors to verify. Direct to the relevant agency or school.": "莫判定居住。列出爱核实个因素。请指引到相关机构或学校。",
        "Do not determine that a household 'is' or 'is not' eligible for Medicaid. Frame as items to verify with the state Medicaid agency. Use 'may apply' and 'rules differ by jurisdiction'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "莫判定一户家「有」或「无」Medicaid 资格。请将其陈述为爱向州 Medicaid 机构核实个项目。请使用「可能适用」佮「规则因管辖区无仝」。请遵循 SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Do not list which states grant in-state tuition for DACA recipients. Frame as classification rules to verify with the school registrar and the state higher-education agency.": "莫列出哪几州对 DACA 受惠者给予本州学费。请将其陈述为爱向学校注册主任佮州高等教育机构核实个分类规则。",
        "Do not provide a public-charge determination or say that using benefits 'will' or 'will not' affect immigration. Frame as 'may interact' and recommend consulting a licensed immigration attorney. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "莫提供公共负担判定或陈述使用福利「会」或「无会」影响移民。请陈述为「可能互动」并建议咨询持证移民律师。请遵循 SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Do not provide medical or transport instructions for controlled substances.": "莫为管制物质提供医疗或运输指示。",
        "Do not provide tactical instructions for transporting, possessing, hiding, storing, modifying, or avoiding enforcement for regulated items.": "莫为受管制物品个运输、持有、隐藏、储存、修改或规避执法,提供战术指示。",
        "Do not provide tax advice. Direct to official tax agency and qualified professionals.": "莫提供税务建议。请指引到官方税务机构佮有资格个专业人士。",
        "Do not provide tax advice. Direct to state tax agency or qualified tax professional.": "莫提供税务建议。请指引到州税务机构或有资格个税务专业人士。",
        "Do not say a Board of Nursing in a particular state grants or refuses an applicant's NCLEX path. Use 'verify with the destination Board of Nursing'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "莫陈述特定州个护理委员会授予或拒绝申请人个 NCLEX 路径。请使用「向目的护理委员会核实」。请遵循 SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Do not say a particular aid program 'is open to' or 'is closed to' DACA recipients or LPRs. Use 'verify with the state aid agency and the school financial-aid office'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "莫陈述特定资助计划「向 DACA 受惠者或 LPR 开放」或「关闭」。请使用「向州资助机构佮学校财务援助办公室核实」。请遵循 SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Do not say a person 'can' or 'cannot' enroll. Use 'verify current eligibility categories with the marketplace operator' since federal rules have changed. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "莫陈述一个人「会当」或「无法」注册。请使用「向市场运营者核实目前个合格类别」,因联邦规则已变更。请遵循 SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Do not state how a specific state defines residency for a given visa category or that someone 'is' a resident. Frame as 'rules differ by jurisdiction' and 'verify with the destination-state tax agency'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "莫陈述特定州按怎为特定签证类别定义居住,或某人「是」居民。请陈述为「规则因管辖区无仝」佮「向目的州税务机关核实」。请遵循 SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Do not state how a specific state defines residency or that someone 'is' a resident. Frame as 'rules differ by jurisdiction' and 'verify with the destination-state tax agency'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "莫陈述特定州按怎定义居住或某人「是」居民。请陈述为「规则因管辖区无仝」佮「向目的州税务机关核实」。请遵循 SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Do not state that any specific board does or does not license a given visa category. Frame everything as items to verify with the destination-state board. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "莫陈述任何特定委员会对特定签证类别核发或无核发执照。一律以爱向目的州委员会核实个项目陈述。请遵循 SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Do not state that any specific board does or does not license non-citizens. Frame everything as items to verify with the destination-state board. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "莫陈述任何特定委员会对非公民核发或无核发执照。一律以爱向目的州委员会核实个项目陈述。请遵循 SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Do not state that any specific person is or is not required to register. Frame as a federal requirement that 'may apply' depending on age and sex, with state implementation details to verify. Use neutral language and follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "莫陈述任何具体人士需要或无需要登记。请将其陈述为可能根据年龄佮性别适用个联邦要求,以及爱核实个州实施细节。请使用中性措辞,并遵循 SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Do not state whether the user is eligible for licensure. Only identify requirements to verify.": "莫陈述使用者是毋是有执照资格。仅识别爱核实个要求。",
        "Do not state which states do or do not issue licenses to a given group, and do not list specific accepted documents. Frame everything as items to verify with the destination-state DMV.": "莫陈述哪几州对特定群体核发或无核发驾照,且莫列出特定可接受文件。一律以爱向目的州 DMV 核实个项目陈述。",
        "Do not state which states issue or do not issue licenses to a given visa category, and do not list specific accepted documents. Frame everything as items to verify with the destination-state DMV. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "莫陈述哪几州对特定签证类别核发或无核发驾照,且莫列出特定可接受文件。一律以爱向目的州 DMV 核实个项目陈述。请遵循 SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Document lists accepted by state DMVs for non-citizen license or state-ID applicants can differ from those accepted for U.S. citizens, and accepted combinations may vary by jurisdiction.": "州 DMV 接受非公民申请驾照或州 ID 个文件清单,可能与美国公民个无仝,且接受组合可能因管辖区无仝。",
        "Documents for proof of identity": "身分证明文件",
        "Done": "完成",
        "Driver's license": "驾照",
        "Driving across one or more state lines for travel.": "为旅行驾车跨越一州或几若州个边界。",
        "Driving with coverage that does not meet destination-state minimums can create compliance and financial problems.": "以无符合目的州最低保额个保险驾驶,可能造成合规佮财务问题。",
        "Drug screen requirements": "药物筛检要求",
        "Edit selections": "编辑选择",
        "Emissions testing requirement": "排放测试要求",
        "Employer policy": "雇主政策",
        "Employment Authorization": "工作授权",
        "Employment paperwork": "雇佣文件",
        "Endorsement requirements if already licensed": "若已持有执照,认可要求",
        "Endorsement, reciprocity, temporary permits, and continuing education requirements vary by state and profession.": "认可、互惠、临时许可证佮继续教育要求,因州佮职业无仝。",
        "Endorsement, reciprocity, temporary practice, and continuing education.": "认可、互惠、临时执业,以及继续教育。",
        "Enhanced or REAL ID": "增强或 REAL ID",
        "Establishing a new permanent residence in the destination state.": "佇目的州建立新个永久居所。",
        "Eviction and late-fee rules": "驱逐佮逾期费规则",
        "Example checklist categories": "示例清单类别",
        "Exploring options. Receive a broad overview checklist.": "探索选项。收着一份广泛个概览清单。",
        "F-1 OPT and STEM OPT specific. Use verify with the DSO and SEVP Portal guidance. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list (legal-conclusion phrasing and penalty-avoidance phrasing). Do not advise on a specific status outcome.": "F-1 OPT 佮 STEM OPT 专属。请使用向 DSO 佮 SEVP Portal 指引核实。请避免 iOS SafeCopy 避免清单(法律结论措辞佮罚则规避措辞)。莫为特定身分结果提供建议。",
        "F-1 specific. Frame as verify with both DSOs and reference Study in the States or ICE materials. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "F-1 专属。陈述为向两个 DSO 核实并参考 Study in the States 或 ICE 资料。请避免 iOS SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "F-1 students on post-completion OPT or a STEM OPT extension generally use the SEVP Portal or work with their DSO to update physical and mailing address, employer information, and other personal data, typically within 10 days of a change. Unemployment-day limits during OPT continue to apply during and after a move.": "F-1 学生在完成后 OPT 或 STEM OPT 延长期间,一般使用 SEVP Portal 或佮 DSO 合作更新实际佮邮寄地址、雇主信息及其他个人资料,通常在变更后 10 工内。OPT 期间个失业工数限制在搬迁期间佮搬迁后继续适用。",
        "F-1, J-1, M-1, and Q specific. Frame as items to verify with IRS guidance and the employer. Do not state that a particular worker is exempt from FICA. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "F-1、J-1、M-1 佮 Q 专属。陈述为爱向 IRS 指引佮雇主核实个项目。莫陈述特定工作者免征 FICA。请避免 iOS SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Factors that may affect residency for tuition, taxes, licensing, benefits.": "可能影响学费、税务、执照、福利个居住因素。",
        "Failing to register on time may affect eligibility for federal benefits, federal jobs, and naturalization later, even though the requirement is federal. State DMV workflows can also trigger automatic registration, which applicants should understand before applying.": "未及时登记可能影响后续联邦福利、联邦职位佮入籍个资格,虽然该要求是联邦个。州 DMV 流程嘛可能触发自动登记,申请人在申请进前应了解此事。",
        "Family move": "家庭搬迁",
        "Federal HealthCare.gov guidance describes a list of immigration statuses considered lawfully present for purposes of the Affordable Care Act marketplace, which includes many common nonimmigrant categories. These categories can purchase coverage without a five-year waiting period that applies in many Medicaid contexts.": "联邦 HealthCare.gov 指引描述被视为《平价医疗法案》市场目的合法在留个移民身分清单,包括真多常见非移民类别。兜类别会当购买保险,无适用于真多 Medicaid 情境个五年等待期。",
        "Federal Medicaid and CHIP rules generally include a five-year waiting period for many qualified non-citizens after obtaining qualified status, with several federal exceptions. States may use an option that removes the waiting period for children and pregnant people, and some states cover certain groups with state funds.": "联邦 Medicaid 佮 CHIP 规则一般包含五年等待期,适用于真多合资格非公民在取得合格身分后,有几个联邦例外。州可能采用选项,移除对囡仔佮孕妇个等待期,而兜州以州资金涵盖某些群体。",
        "Federal Medicare guidance generally describes eligibility for non-citizens who are lawfully admitted for permanent residence and have lived in the United States for five continuous years. Federal Medicaid rules for most nonimmigrants are narrower than for LPRs, with state-specific options for emergency Medicaid and for lawfully residing children and pregnant individuals.": "联邦 Medicare 指引一般描述对合法获准永久居留并在美国连续居住五年个非公民个资格。联邦 Medicaid 规则对大部分非移民较 LPR 狭窄,有州专属个紧急 Medicaid 选项,以及对合法居住个囡仔佮孕妇个选项。",
        "Federal REAL ID rules require evidence of lawful status, and many states issue a REAL ID to nonimmigrant visa holders only with an expiration date that does not extend past the I-94, the visa, or another underlying federal document. Implementation differs between states, and standard (non-REAL-ID) options may or may not be offered.": "联邦 REAL ID 规则要求合法身分个证据,而真多州对非移民签证持有人核发 REAL ID,到期日不会超出 I-94、签证或其他底层联邦文件。各州实施无仝,标准(非 REAL ID)选项可能提供或无提供。",
        "Federal SNAP, TANF, and similar programs apply a waiting period to many qualified non-citizens. Some states use state funds to operate replacement or supplemental programs that cover groups not eligible for the federal program, with differing rules.": "联邦 SNAP、TANF 及相似计划对真多合资格非公民适用等待期。兜州运用州资金运营替代或补充计划,涵盖无合格联邦计划个群体,规则无仝。",
        "Federal law": "联邦法",
        "Federal law (INA section 265) generally directs non-citizens to report a change of address to USCIS within 10 days of moving, typically through Form AR-11 or the USCIS online change-of-address tool. The federal filing is separate from updating a state DMV record, an employer, a school, or the U.S. Postal Service.": "联邦法(INA 第 265 条)一般要求非公民在搬厝后 10 工内向 USCIS 报告地址变更,通常透过表格 AR-11 或 USCIS 在线地址变更工具。该联邦申报与更新州 DMV 记录、雇主、学校或美国邮政服务个程序无仝。",
        "Federal law generally requires motor vehicle offices to offer voter registration to applicants, and forms are screened for citizenship attestations. Non-citizens generally are not eligible to register for federal elections, and a registration record can later create immigration complications.": "联邦法一般要求机动车辆办公室向申请人提供选民登记,且表格会查核公民身分声明。非公民一般无资格登记联邦选举,而登记记录可能后摆产生移民问题。",
        "Federal residency for tax purposes determines whether worldwide income is reported, which IRS forms apply, and how an interstate move's first and last year are filed at the federal level, separately from state residency rules.": "联邦税务居住判定是否报告全球收入、适用啥物 IRS 表格,以及跨州搬迁个第一年佮最后一年按怎在联邦层级申报,与州居住规则分开。",
        "Federal rules govern which immigration statuses can purchase coverage and receive financial help through the Affordable Care Act marketplace, and those rules have changed. State-based marketplaces and state-funded programs add another layer that can differ between origin and destination.": "联邦规则规定啥物移民身分会当透过《平价医疗法案》市场购买保险佮收着财务协助,且兜规则已变更。州市场佮州资助计划增加另一层,可能在出发州佮目的州间无仝。",
        "Federal tax authority": "联邦税务机关",
        "Federal tax authority general guidance": "联邦税务机关一般指引",
        "Filing Requirements, Residency, and Telecommuting FAQs": "申报要求、居住佮远端办公 FAQ",
        "Flags risk levels so you know where to focus": "标示风险等级,你知影爱将焦点摆佗位",
        "Florida Board of Governors page on residency for tuition purposes for the State University System. flbog.edu returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative.": "Florida Board of Governors 关于州大学系统学费居住个页面。flbog.edu 对非浏览器请求返回 403(Cloudflare);这是已知误判。",
        "Florida FLHSMV documentation page for nonimmigrant applicants for driver licenses and identification cards.": "Florida FLHSMV 对非移民驾照佮身分识别卡申请人个文件页。",
        "Follow device language": "跟随设备语言",
        "For L-1, whether the new worksite is the same qualifying U.S. office described in the petition or a different one": "对 L-1,新工作地点是否为请愿中描述个相仝合格美国办公室或其他办公室",
        "For L-1A, L-1B, and O-1 status, USCIS treats a move to a new worksite as a material change in some fact patterns and not others, depending on what the original petition described and whether the new location is consistent with the approved terms. The analysis follows the underlying petition, not LCA-based MSA rules.": "对 L-1A、L-1B 佮 O-1 身分,USCIS 在某些事实模式中将工作地点搬迁视为重大变更,在某些则否,取决于原始请愿描述个内容,以及新地点是否与已批准条件一致。该分析遵循底层请愿,毋是依 LCA 个 MSA 规则。",
        "For O-1, whether the new venue, event, engagement, or agent arrangement falls within the approved petition scope": "对 O-1,新场地、活动、聘约或经纪安排是否落在已批准请愿范围内",
        "For federal tax purposes, a non-citizen is generally treated as a resident alien if they meet the Substantial Presence Test or hold lawful permanent resident status, with separate rules in IRS Publication 519 for exempt individuals (such as certain F-1, J-1, M-1, and Q students and scholars) whose days of presence may not count.": "在联邦税务目的上,非公民一般在符合实质居留测试或持有合法永久居民身分时被视为居民外国人,IRS Publication 519 对豁免个人(例如某些 F-1、J-1、M-1 佮 Q 学生佮学者)有单独规则,伊个停留工数可能无算。",
        "For nursing specifically, how the destination state treats primary state of residency under the Nurse Licensure Compact for a non-citizen who declares either the country of origin or the compact state, and any credentials-evaluation requirement (for example, CGFNS) for internationally educated applicants": "护理具体而言,目的州按怎对待 Nurse Licensure Compact 中非公民在声明原籍国或互惠州为主要居住州时个主要居住州,以及国际教育申请人个学历评估要求(例如 CGFNS)",
        "Form AR-11 paper version posted on uscis.gov.": "刊登在 uscis.gov 上个表格 AR-11 纸本版。",
        "Frame AR-11 as a federal reporting step to verify, not a guarantee of status. Do not state that any specific status category is or is not covered without source. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list (legal-conclusion phrasing such as the i-word, the p-words, and penalty-avoidance phrasing). Direct readers to consult a licensed immigration attorney for status-specific guidance.": "将 AR-11 陈述为爱核实个联邦报告步骤,毋是身分保证。莫无来源陈述任何具体身分类别被涵盖或无涵盖。请避免 iOS SafeCopy 避免清单(法律结论措辞,例如 i 字、p 字佮罚则规避措辞)。请指引读者咨询持证移民律师以获得身分专属指引。",
        "Frame as a federal requirement that may apply, with a nonimmigrant exception that may apply based on continuous valid status. Do not state that any specific person is or is not required to register. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "陈述为可能适用个联邦要求,以及可能基于连续有效身分适用个非移民例外。莫陈述任何具体人士需要或无需要登记。请避免 iOS SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Frame as items to verify in IRS Publication 519 and with a qualified tax preparer. Do not state a person is a dual-status filer for a particular year. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "陈述为爱在 IRS Publication 519 佮有资格个税务准备人员核实个项目。莫陈述某人特定年度是双重身分申报人。请避免 iOS SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Frame as items to verify with CMS and the destination-state Medicaid agency. Federal rules have changed and may continue to change. Do not state a person is or is not eligible. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "陈述为爱向 CMS 佮目的州 Medicaid 机构核实个项目。联邦规则已变更,且可能继续变更。莫陈述某人合格或无合格。请避免 iOS SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Frame as items to verify with IRS Publication 519 and a tax preparer. Do not state a person is or is not a resident alien for federal tax purposes. Use may apply and rules differ by jurisdiction. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "陈述为爱向 IRS Publication 519 佮税务准备人员核实个项目。莫陈述某人在联邦税务目的上「是」或「无是」居民外国人。请使用「可能适用」佮「规则因管辖区无仝」。请避免 iOS SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Frame as items to verify with the DSO or J-1 sponsor and Study in the States or ICE guidance. This item is specific to F-1, M-1, and J-1 status. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list (legal-conclusion phrasing and penalty-avoidance phrasing).": "陈述为爱向 DSO 或 J-1 赞助方佮 Study in the States 或 ICE 指引核实个项目。此项目专属于 F-1、M-1 佮 J-1 身分。请避免 iOS SafeCopy 避免清单(法律结论措辞佮罚则规避措辞)。",
        "Frame as items to verify with the current HealthCare.gov or state-based marketplace lists. Do not state any specific category is or is not on the lawfully present list, since federal rules have changed. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "陈述为爱向目前 HealthCare.gov 或州市场清单核实个项目。莫陈述任何特定类别在合法在留清单上或无在,因联邦规则已变更。请避免 iOS SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Full disclaimer:": "完整免责声明:",
        "General information only. Not legal advice. Verify with official sources.": "干焦一般信息。毋是法律建议。请向官方来源核实。",
        "General information only. Verify with the relevant official source. Not legal advice.": "干焦一般信息。请向相关官方来源核实。毋是法律建议。",
        "Generate checklist": "产生清单",
        "Generated:": "产生:",
        "Generates a checklist of topics to verify before moving": "产生一份搬厝进前爱核实个主题清单",
