        "MoveSafe provides general legal and administrative information based on publicly available sources. It does not provide legal advice, does not create an attorney-client relationship, and should not be used as a substitute for advice from a licensed attorney in your jurisdiction. Laws and agency rules change frequently. Always verify information with official sources before making decisions.": "MoveSafe 基于公开来源提供一般个法律佮行政信息。伊无提供法律建议,无建立律师-当事人关系,且无应作为你管辖区持照律师建议个替代品。法律佮机构规则时常变更。决策进前,请永远向官方来源核实信息。",
