        "Under 22 CFR Part 62, J-1 program sponsors maintain the SEVIS record and monitor the site of activity for each exchange visitor. A move that changes residence, site of activity, or host organization generally triggers an exchange-visitor reporting obligation to the sponsor and a sponsor update to SEVIS.": "根据 22 CFR 第 62 部分,J-1 计划赞助方维护 SEVIS 记录并监控每位交流访客个活动场地。涉及住所、活动场地或主办机构变更个搬迁,一般触发对赞助方个交流访客报告义务,以及赞助方对 SEVIS 个更新。",
        "Under USCIS guidance following Matter of Simeio Solutions (2015), an H-1B worker's move to a worksite outside the metropolitan statistical area (MSA) or area of intended employment listed on the current Labor Condition Application (LCA) is generally a material change that calls for a new LCA and an amended H-1B petition.": "在 Matter of Simeio Solutions(2015)之后,根据 USCIS 指引,H-1B 工作者搬到目前劳工条件申请(LCA)所列大都市统计区(MSA)或目标就业区域之外个工作地点,一般属于重大变更,要求新个 LCA 佮修订个 H-1B 请愿。",
